From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ondrej Jirman <megi@xff.cz>
Date: Wed, 11 Feb 2026 21:20:20 +0100
Subject: ARM: dts: allwinner: Increase clock-latency-ns to 2ms

Real time needed for OPP change must include voltage regulator update
delay and other delays.
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-a83t.dtsi | 20 +++++-----
 arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-h3.dtsi   | 18 ++++-----
 2 files changed, 19 insertions(+), 19 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-a83t.dtsi b/arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-a83t.dtsi
index 111111111111..222222222222 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-a83t.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-a83t.dtsi
@@ -207,31 +207,31 @@ cpu0_opp_table: opp-table-cluster0 {
 		opp-480000000 {
 			opp-hz = /bits/ 64 <480000000>;
 			opp-microvolt = <840000>;
-			clock-latency-ns = <244144>; /* 8 32k periods */
+			clock-latency-ns = <2000000>;
 		};
 
 		opp-1008000000 {
 			opp-hz = /bits/ 64 <1008000000>;
 			opp-microvolt = <840000>;
-			clock-latency-ns = <244144>; /* 8 32k periods */
